Subject: Piratical Romeo and Juliet
Description: Come see three fierce pirates, showing off their skills as they pirate everyone's favorite bard, Shakespeare! Captain Duckman, his bride/first Mate Jenniveve, and new cabin girl Titania are out to provide their take on Romeo and Juliet, in a short and funny manner. It's a Rennaissance Faire style interactive show!  Speakers include:Jennifer Peters, Katherine Hatfield-Nix, Mitchell Peters, Jennifer Reisbig - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
